item.title: Spring Magic Me With A Calmer More Meditative Mind
item.description: The mind wants to come in and be part of our lives, but if the chatter is going on constantly, there is no time to be present and hence harness our 5D potential. Mindfulness practices are a way to turn up your vibratory rate. Learn about how to make meditation more accessible as well as the scared art of the senses when The Gentle Yoga Warrior interviews Blair Abee! Blair is an author, poet, educator, consultant and ordinary mystic... Feed: https://feeds.buzzsprout.com/1144574.rss
